p: In addition, the results showed that pretreatment with exogenous ETHE1 or ACY-3 protein could increase the survival rate of HEK293 cells after DU exposure, and the effect of exogenous ETHE1 seemed to be more significant ( Fig. 3d). Calcein-AM/PI staining also showed that exogenous ETHE1 or ACY-3 protein could reduce the number of dead cells induced by DU ( Fig. 3e). These findings indicated that ACY-3 and ETHE1 might involve in protection roles of MT.
